questiondata.strat-other: I for the most part noticed that most words fit into categories, such as fruit, things in a gardenpeople, occupations, and food, to name a few. I found it much easier this way.Because the words were presented fairly quickly, i for the most part didn't have time to create some type of visual image in my head(as I often do in order to remember words more easily. Having no distractions sure helped!
